What variables need to be passed into this?

-Jumbotron with name, rank, ph#, wep#, #AT missions, #AT miles
current active mission(if applicable)

list of any special statuses
<btn to add a status>

list of missions - this should be refactored into a display helper
(blue:upcoming / green:ongoing / red:late / strike:completed)

display needs to be passed
- Soldier
